>渲染机制&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>虚拟DOM，Virtual DOM&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hash路由和History路由</title><link>https://inshomepgup.github.io/blog-hugo-stack/programming/frontend/vue/vuerouter/hash%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%92%8Chistory%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://inshomepgup.github.io/blog-hugo-stack/programming/frontend/vue/vuerouter/hash%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%92%8Chistory%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1/</guid><description>&lt;p>监听hash改变的函数
